<p>

<b>Tony Plana</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../ury/22nd_century.xml">
April 19</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../865/34865.xml">
1953</link><ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> or <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../982/34982.xml">
1954</link>) is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../629/1172629.xml">
Cuban-American</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../753/753.xml">
actor</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../078/103078.xml">
director</link>. He currently plays <fictional_character wordnetid="109587565" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../153/6985153.xml">
Betty Suarez</link></fictional_character>
's father, <fictional_character wordnetid="109587565" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../577/7019577.xml">
Ignacio Suarez</link></fictional_character>
, on the <network wordnetid="108434259" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../027/62027.xml">
ABC</link></network>
 show <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../430/4874430.xml">
Ugly Betty</link></series>
.</it></p>

<sec>
<st>
Biography</st>

<ss1>
<st>
Personal life</st>
<p>

Plana was born in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../719/49719.xml">
Havana</link></village>
. His family moved to <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../846/53846.xml">
Miami</link> in 1963.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> He is a graduate of <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../934/196934.xml">
Loyola Marymount University</link></university>
 and was trained in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../032/2032.xml">
acting</link> at the <school wordnetid="108276720" confidence="0.8">
<educational_institution wordnetid="108276342" confidence="0.8">
<institution wordnetid="108053576" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../026/163026.xml">
Royal Academy of Dramatic Art</link></institution>
</educational_institution>
</school>
 in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/17867.xml">
London</link></village>
, <autocracy wordnetid="108361001" confidence="0.8">
<system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<political_orientation wordnetid="106212839" confidence="0.8">
<monarchy wordnetid="108363812" confidence="0.8">
<state wordnetid="108168978" confidence="0.8">
<political_unit wordnetid="108359949" confidence="0.8">
