<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../945/654945.xml">
Cagney &amp; Lacey</link></series>
</it> and many others. </p>
<p>

Plana has acted in films such as <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../539/242539.xml">
An Officer and a Gentleman</link></it>, <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../971/905971.xml">
